casebody.head_matter:
Michael Paul PUZEY, Petitioner
v.
UNITED STATES
No. 19-5304
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
